name: Standard Colours
description: This is a collection of some pre-baked common colours. RGB values are based on the 16 colours defined in HTML standard.
contents: Aqua - Returns the colour aqua., Fuchsia - Returns the colour fuchsia a.k.a. magenta., Grey - Returns the colour grey., Maroon - Returns the colour maroon., Navy - Returns the colour navy., Olive - Returns the colour olive., Silver - Returns the colour silver., Teal - Returns the colour teal., Yellow - Returns the colour yellow., Purple - Returns the colour purple., Lime - Returns the colour lime., Blue - Returns the colour blue., Black - Returns the colour black., White - Returns the colour white., Red - Returns the colour red., Green - Returns the colour green.
